						<p>Records that the Śivabrāhmaṇas Avināsi Kāḻiyaṉ and three others received 24 <hi rend="italic">āṉaiachchu Śriyakki-paḻañjalāgai</hi> from the treasury of the temple at Tirumuruganpūṇḍi and agreed to burn four perpetual lamps at the temple.</p>						

